name: Experiment Or Die #51
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. Still working over the top of yesterdays design and again the colors got wild with tonights piece. The crazy lines from this test print I made years ago in contrast to the main typography are really speaking to me. There doesn't seem to be any 1 path through the NFT space and it will likely be a meandering journey and don't let anyone or anything deter you. You've got to be determined and stay on your path no matter where it takes you.
